WEBVTT

00:01.672 --> 00:03.319
There's always been
some thing,

00:03.344 --> 00:05.134
like a dark cloud
hanging over me.

00:05.484 --> 00:06.890
I've ignored it, I've denied it,

00:07.008 --> 00:09.008
but it's...
it's always been there.

00:09.009 --> 00:11.789
RENEUS: 666.

00:11.852 --> 00:13.311
Does that mean anything
to you?

00:13.312 --> 00:14.101
[Dogs barking]

00:14.126 --> 00:15.616
WOMAN:
When Reneus was killed,

00:15.641 --> 00:17.851
the cops say he was mauled
by some animal.

00:19.835 --> 00:22.455
[Screams]
Somebody got me!

00:25.266 --> 00:27.555
Two accidents
in the past few days.

00:27.556 --> 00:28.484
Pretty weird.

00:28.547 --> 00:30.539
MAN:
We know he's here.

00:30.578 --> 00:33.421
It's one of the seven daggers
of Megiddo.

00:33.523 --> 00:36.312
Strike where the heart
should be.

00:36.313 --> 00:37.863
[Knocking on door]

00:40.193 --> 00:41.403
[Grunting]

00:44.863 --> 00:46.693
[Screams]

00:47.570 --> 00:49.203
The man that tried
to kill you,

00:49.281 --> 00:51.071
he had one of these,
didn't he?

00:52.031 --> 00:53.861
Come with me.

00:57.441 --> 00:59.361
Welcome home, Damien.

01:03.741 --> 01:05.821
[Siren wails in distance]

01:09.481 --> 01:12.611
[Phone ringing]

01:12.953 --> 01:14.742
Detective Jim Shay?

01:14.743 --> 01:17.782
- James.
- I brought you a copy of my file

01:17.783 --> 01:19.082
about that professor that was
mauled the other night.

01:19.083 --> 01:20.759
Uh, yeah.
Thank you.

01:20.830 --> 01:22.087
Yeah, I was just
swinging through.

01:22.252 --> 01:23.672
I'm meeting some guys
for drinks.

01:23.673 --> 01:25.541
- Glad I caught you.
- Christ, what a mess.

01:25.542 --> 01:27.867
Look at that body...
throat ripped out,

01:27.892 --> 01:29.721
teeth marks right down
to the bone.

01:29.722 --> 01:31.775
It's a brutal way to go
for a biblical scholar.

01:31.791 --> 01:33.380
Look where all that learning
got him.

01:33.381 --> 01:34.840
My parents tried
to raise me Catholic,

01:34.841 --> 01:36.630
I told them they could keep
their guilt.

01:36.631 --> 01:39.041
Yeah, you never told me
how your taxi accident

01:39.042 --> 01:40.453
connects with
this dog mauling.

01:40.554 --> 01:43.380
My deceased was a grad student
of this Reneus.

01:43.381 --> 01:45.710
He was killed while trying
to stab somebody.

01:46.335 --> 01:47.766
You have any idea how a pack
of wild dogs

01:47.791 --> 01:50.296
got into your dead professor's
office in the first place?

01:50.321 --> 01:52.710
Well, Reneus had a couple of
visitors earlier that evening.

01:52.711 --> 01:55.040
I'm trying to reach them to
corroborate the time lines.

01:55.041 --> 01:56.580
Hmm,
they give you anything?

01:56.581 --> 01:58.460
I spoke briefly to one the night
of the attack.

01:58.461 --> 01:59.960
I'm still waiting for her
to call me back.

01:59.961 --> 02:01.380
Do you have their names?

02:01.381 --> 02:04.630
Uh, yeah.
A reporter... Kelly Baptiste.

02:04.631 --> 02:06.130
Yeah, she ain't calling.

02:06.131 --> 02:08.669
She died the same night...
another freak accident.

02:08.670 --> 02:11.631
The other visitor,
let me guess.

02:12.453 --> 02:13.380
Damien Thorn?

02:13.381 --> 02:15.580
You know him?

02:15.581 --> 02:17.460
- Yeah.
- [Panting]

02:17.461 --> 02:18.920
Thanks for coming by.

02:18.921 --> 02:21.000
Yeah, sure thing.

02:21.001 --> 02:24.001
♪♪

